The paper focuses on video summarization, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves computing similarity between video shots and query, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which can be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG).
